        "action": "Restrict the serving \u201cterms\u201d of an MP in the UK Parliament to three.",
        "additional_details": "Many professions include enforced \u201cretirements\u201d reflecting changes to their operational environments.\r\nAlso reducing the political term would reduce the commercial advantage of operating in the political environment, which would also benefit standards applicable to the House of Commons.",
        "background": "The American constitution restricts their President to retire after serving two terms. With the world changing so much, is now the time to consider reform of Westminster to improve its effectiveness. \r\nDoes the electorate control the politicians or do the politicians control the electorate?",
